name: Vintage Pentax ME (35mm Film SLR)
description:
I have a near-mint condition Pentax ME for sale, which is a superb 35mm camera for student photographers and hobbyists.

The camera does not come with a lens cap, since I'm possibly the 3rd owner of this camera. The filter screen has very tiny scratches on it, but it does not affect the actual photos nor does it obstruct your view. 

The camera comes with a brand new roll of 35mm color film.

The camera will receive a final thorough cleaning before shipment.

name: Spot It!
description:
Spot it! is the addictive, feverishly fun matching game for every generation. The first thing to know about Spot it! is that there is always one, and only one, matching symbol between any two cards. Got it? Now all you need is a sharp eye and a quick hand to play all five party games packed into the grab 'n' go tin. Including up to eight players, Spot it! is a cinch to learn, plays fast, and is irresistibly fun for all ages!

--

Seller's Note: This is such a simple yet fun game. Anyone, regardless of age, will love it.
